name: test_app_deepfry_get
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool image.
Tool description: a powerful and fast Image manipulation. Perfect for discord bots or web apps. https://dagpi.xyz
API description: Sends a GET request to the deepfry endpoint of the RapidAPI Image Processing service with the specified URL and API key.

url.description: The URL of the image that you want to deepfry. Defaults to 'https://dagbot-is.the-be.st/logo.png'.
